"2024-07-02T14:18:55Z","body":"Agroal documentation defines the feature as follows:\r\n\r\n> Allows connection validation prior to acquisition (foreground validation) overriding any idle timeout. Because of the overhead of performing validation on every call, itâ€™s recommended to rely on idle validation instead\r\n\r\nSource: https://agroal.github.io/docs.html\r\n\r\nSo from what I understand, usually Agroal would only validate connections when they've been idle for a while, and this instead forces validation on every single retrieval of a connection from the pool?\r\n\r\nCan you please give us an example of a use case for that, for the record?","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/comments/2203349704/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"yrodiere","id":412878,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxMjg3OA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/412878?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere","html_url":"https://github.com/yrodiere","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yrodiere/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/comments/2203350564","html_url":"https://github.com/quarkusio/